---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Getting Started"
  description="Get started with THG Commerce products"
>
  <Navigation slot="sidebar" />
  
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Quick Start Guide</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300 mb-6">
        Welcome to THG Commerce documentation. This guide will help you get started with our commerce solutions.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-stone-800 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-700">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">1. Choose Your Solution</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300 mb-4">
            Browse our products to find the right solution for your business needs:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300 space-y-2">
            <li><a href="/products/storefronts" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">Storefronts</a> - Build your commerce experience</li>
            <li><a href="/products/insights" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">Insights</a> - Track user interactions</li>
            <li><a href="/products/checkout" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">Checkout</a> - Secure payment processing</li>
            <li><a href="/products/search" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">Search</a> - Powerful search capabilities</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-stone-800 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-700">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2. Set Up Your Environment</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300 mb-4">
            Each product has its own setup requirements. Common prerequisites include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300 space-y-2">
            <li>Node.js 18 or higher</li>
            <li>npm or yarn package manager</li>
            <li>Git for version control</li>
            <li>API keys (product specific)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Integration Options</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-stone-800 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-700">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">API-First</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300">
            Direct integration with our RESTful and GraphQL APIs for maximum flexibility.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-stone-800 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-700">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">SDKs</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300">
            Official SDKs for popular frameworks and platforms.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-stone-800 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-700">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Components</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300">
            Pre-built UI components and packages for rapid development.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Next Steps</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <a href="/docs/storefronts" class="block p-4 bg-white dark:bg-stone-800 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-700 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Build Your Storefront →</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300">Create a custom commerce experience with our Storefront solutions.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/docs/insights/installation" class="block p-4 bg-white dark:bg-stone-800 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-700 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Set Up Analytics →</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300">Start tracking user interactions with Insights.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/resources/best-practices" class="block p-4 bg-white dark:bg-stone-800 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-700 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Learn Best Practices →</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300">Discover patterns and practices for building successful commerce experiences.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</PageLayout>